article_title: Brooklyn, Deadline Approaching to Register to Vote in U.S. Presidential Primary!

article_metadata.description: The U.S. presidential primary election is on April 19, 2016-- one month away-- and you have exactly one week left, until March 25, 2016, to register to vote.
